	Prioritized Starting List

	If you want to start with \u201cjust what you absolutely must have\u201d (given your existing gear), here\u2019s a minimal subset to order first:

	Wort Chiller (immersion or plate)

	Thermometer / temperature probe

	Transfer tubing / hoses + hose clamps / fittings

	Hydrometer (or refractometer) + test jar

	Cleaner + no-rinse sanitizer

	Airlock / bung / blow-off hose

	Digital scale

	Kegging hardware (if you plan to keg): CO\u2082 + regulator + kegs + lines / disconnects

	Bottling hardware (if you plan to bottle): bottles + caps + capper + filler wand

	Once you have those, you\u2019ll be able to brew your first batches. After that, you can gradually add \u201cnice extras\u201d (pH meter, yeast starters, extra fermenters, insulation, automation, etc.).